{"cf_tracking_thunderbird_esr52": "---", "status": "RESOLVED", "cf_tracking_firefox60": "---", "attachments": [{"creator": "jseward@acm.org", "is_obsolete": 0, "is_patch": 1, "flags": [{"status": "+", "name": "review", "modification_date": "2014-11-19T16:11:03Z", "type_id": 4, "creation_date": "2014-11-19T09:57:35Z", "id": 1037333, "setter": "nchen@mozilla.com"}], "content_type": "text/plain", "id": 8525212}], "classification": "Components", "creator": "jseward@acm.org", "cc": ["nchen@mozilla.com"], "depends_on": [], "creation_time": "2014-11-18T12:05:59Z", "cf_user_story": "", "cf_tracking_firefox_relnote": "---", "platform": "All", "cf_status_firefox58": "---", "cf_status_firefox59": "---", "keywords": [], "summary": "For MacOS builds running on Valgrind, make ThreadStackHelper::GetStack be a no-op", "id": 1100911, "assigned_to_detail": {"email": "jseward@acm.org", "id": 346453, "name": "jseward@acm.org", "real_name": "Julian Seward [:jseward]"}, "severity": "normal", "is_confirmed": true, "is_creator_accessible": true, "cf_has_regression_range": "---", "assigned_to": "jseward@acm.org", "comment_count": 5, "comments": [{"text": "When running Firefox on Valgrind on MacOSX 10.9 and possibily 10.10,\nthe syscalls thread_suspend and thread_resume cause Valgrind to hang,\nin ThreadStackHelper::GetStack(Stack& aStack) in ThreadStackHelper.cpp.\nDespite considerable investigation, the reasons for the hang are unknown.\nThere is no problem when not running on Valgrind, so I assume this is\na problem in Valgrind itself.\n\nProposed fix is to make GetStack return without doing anything when\nrunning on MacOS *and* this is a --enable-valgrind build.  Will have no\neffect on release builds, nor on --enable-valgrind builds running \"natively\".", "author": "jseward@acm.org", "id": 9604643, "time": "2014-11-18T12:05:59Z"}, {"text": "That sounds reasonable. You can also return false from ThreadStackHelper::PrepareStackBuffer to make GetStack return early.\n\nDo we run tests under Valgrind? If we do, you may have to disable test_ThreadHangStats.js.", "author": "nchen@mozilla.com", "id": 9605498, "time": "2014-11-18T16:14:52Z"}, {"text": "Created attachment 8525212\nbug1100911-1.diff", "author": "jseward@acm.org", "id": 9610187, "time": "2014-11-19T09:57:35Z"}, {"text": "https://hg.mozilla.org/integration/mozilla-inbound/rev/ffca01c1afea", "author": "jseward@acm.org", "id": 9618979, "time": "2014-11-20T22:40:22Z"}, {"text": "https://hg.mozilla.org/mozilla-central/rev/ffca01c1afea", "author": "cbook@mozilla.com", "id": 9621398, "time": "2014-11-21T12:02:10Z"}], "cf_last_resolved": "2014-11-21T12:02:10Z", "priority": "--", "mentors_detail": [], "cf_crash_signature": "", "version": "Trunk", "cf_qa_whiteboard": "", "cf_tracking_firefox_esr52": "---", "cf_tracking_firefox59": "---", "last_change_time": "2014-11-21T12:02:10Z", "cf_platform_rel": "---", "product": "Core", "cf_status_firefox_esr52": "---", "blocks": [], "qa_contact": "", "see_also": [], "cf_fx_iteration": "---", "component": "XPCOM", "votes": 0, "groups": [], "cf_status_firefox60": "---", "target_milestone": "mozilla36", "is_cc_accessible": true, "cf_status_thunderbird_esr52": "---", "url": "", "creator_detail": {"email": "jseward@acm.org", "id": 346453, "name": "jseward@acm.org", "real_name": "Julian Seward [:jseward]"}, "whiteboard": "", "mentors": [], "cc_detail": [{"email": "nchen@mozilla.com", "id": 281508, "name": "nchen@mozilla.com", "real_name": "Jim Chen [:jchen] [:darchons]"}], "cf_has_str": "---", "alias": null, "dupe_of": null, "flags": [], "cf_tracking_firefox58": "---", "cf_rank": null, "is_open": false, "history": [{"changes": [{"field_name": "flagtypes.name", "removed": "", "attachment_id": 8525212, "added": "review?(nchen@mozilla.com)"}], "who": "jseward@acm.org", "when": "2014-11-19T09:57:35Z"}, {"changes": [{"field_name": "flagtypes.name", "removed": "review?(nchen@mozilla.com)", "attachment_id": 8525212, "added": "review+"}], "who": "nchen@mozilla.com", "when": "